Package: TSrepr
Type: Package
Title: Representation methods for time series
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Peter", "Laurinec", email = "tsreprpackage@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Methods for representations of time series to help more accurate and effective time series data mining.
    Non-data adaptive, data adaptive, model-based and data dictated representation methods implemented. Also min-max and z-score normalizations, and forecasting accuracy measures are implemented.
